<h1 id='monetary-system'>Monetary System</h1>
<p>The Ardor Monetary System features a special asset class currency secured by the Ardor network and blockchain. Virtual currencies with a variety of customizable properties can be created in minutes.</p>

<p>The API calls below help create and also exchange and manage your created virtual currency.</p>
